uk.gov.nationalarchives.droid
Interface JHOVE2IAnalysisController

All Known Implementing Classes:
DROIDAnalysisController
public interface JHOVE2IAnalysisController

Reverse-engineered interface to captures static constants fields used by various DROID classes Static fields are a copy of methods from class uk.gov.nationalarchives.droid in the UK National Archives DROID distribution. Method signatures are intended to facilitate caching of parsed DROID configuration and signature files.

Author:
smorrissey
